*Stvarno* sam zaboravio svoj domaći zadatak. (I really forgot my homework.)
*Stvarno* nije bilo lako. (It really wasn't easy.)
*Stvarno* si se odlično snašao. (You really managed great.)
Nisam *stvarno* mislio da ćeš to uraditi. (I didn't really think you'd do that.)
*Stvarno* me je iznenadilo. (It really surprised me.)
Nisam *stvarno* znala da to postoji. (I didn't really know that exists.)